rs $250+.<\/p><p>Regular International parcels take approximately 3 weeks. <\/p><p>Express shipping option available at checkout for $30 AUD.<\/p><p>Please read more of our Shipping Policy <a href=\"\/policies\/shipping-policy\" title=\"Shipping Policy\">here.<\/a><\/p><p>RETURNS\/EXCHANGES<\/p><p>We accept exchanges or returns for change of mind, as long as it is processed within 14 days.<\/p><p>Please follow instructions on our  <a href=\"https:\/\/www.oceansoulbali.com\/policies\/refund-policy\" title=\"https:\/\/www.oceansoulbali.com\/policies\/refund-policy\">Returns <\/a>page.<\/p><p>WARRANTY<\/p><p>We stand by the quality of our swimsuits, they are tailor made with high quality Italian fabric. <\/p><p>We offer a 12 month warranty from date of purchase, shall the make, material or hardware malfunction.<\/p><p>Read more about our warranty <a href=\"\/pages\/warranty\" title=\"Warranty\">here.<\/a><\/p>","default_open_accordion":false}},"0f909705-4368-4514-8d5e-71a0ac76a5cb":{"type":"accordion_content","settings":{"section_class":"section_class","page":"","title":"Contact Us","text":"<p>Have a question? You can reach us below or on live chat.<\/p><p><a href=\"mailto:customercare@oceansoulbali.com\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"mailto:customercare@oceansoulbali.com\">Email<\/a><\/p><p><a href=\"http:\/\/wa.me\/61407215854\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"http:\/\/wa.me\/61407215854\">Whats App<\/a><\/p><p><\/p>","default_open_accordion":false}}},"block_order":["judge_me_reviews_preview_badge_Uqxx97","product_variants","product_quantity","518bdfc4-e6a0-4562-ad4e-a749a84096b2","c76af5a1-ddb2-4df8-a229-edef90940010","7083fa5a-a988-498e-ac51-81c70cca09d2","5a0481c6-7b6b-45dc-99cf-3aca7980daa4","product_buttons","tolstoy_shoppable_video_ugc_stories_block_nkc7Nb","2bee718c-a25a-4b01-996c-9678953bbf0a","b21287a0-71ea-48e4-95a5-e30b5c121dc2","876a735f-f0bb-4624-b8cc-8d60db6ba807","ac9f6f7c-33c1-4256-932e-3bd4272452e2","49935d06-a61f-4be4-865c-9762a9f134a3","product_description",