838275a57a97e2":{"type":"apps","blocks":{"judge_me_reviews_review_widget_dnn9wA":{"type":"shopify:\/\/apps\/judge-me-reviews\/blocks\/review_widget\/61ccd3b1-a9f2-4160-9fe9-4fec8413e5d8","settings":{}}},"block_order":["judge_me_reviews_review_widget_dnn9wA"],"settings":{"display_wide":false}},"product-content":{"type":"main-product-content","blocks":{"28dd0a33-d199-4642-860b-b3860292a2ba":{"type":"shopify:\/\/apps\/judge-me-reviews\/blocks\/ugc_media_grid\/61ccd3b1-a9f2-4160-9fe9-4fec8413e5d8","settings":{}}},"block_order":["28dd0a33-d199-4642-860b-b3860292a2ba"],"disabled":true,"settings":{"background":"#f9f9f9","allow_multiple":false}},"ffd7507a-dce2-40e6-af87-0e8a295f7ef6":{"type":"editorial-columns","blocks":{"8743bf57-6b1a-4f8c-8988-5e42ae277901":{"type":"text_block","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Untitled_f9ddb395-843c-4ce9-8df6-f4d27f3560a4.jpg","link":"","title_text":"The Perfect one piece","text":"<p>Our two piece bikinis are made with  a luxurious sustainable buttery soft fabric. <br\/>They are the perfect intersection of sporty and fashionable.  With a comfortable seamless design, both functional and flattering paired with a tailored feminine design that is suitable for leisure or athletic activities.<\/p>","button_text":"Button"}},"a5eb81f9-4c92-4ecc-bf0a-6c9cf53eb6cf":{"type":"text_block","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Square_naut.png","link":"","title_text":"Designed for comfort","text":"<p>We’ve designed our swimsuits for comfort right down to the smallest detail.  The luxuriously soft fabric, double lined, with innovative cupless support and smooth seams will hold you in and support you, with all your water activities.<\/p>","button_text":"Button"}},"167e640a-03e8-48de-b93f-07bbc26e1244":{"type":"text_block","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Ocean_Soul_Bali_Sustainable_Swimwear_Sustainable_Fabric.jpg","link":"","title_text":"Sustainable Swim","text":"<p>We value slow fashion over fast with a focus on sustainable fabrics and ethical production. Crafted from regenerated nylon that is designed to last twice as long as your regular swimsuit. Our swimwear is designed & made in Bali with love, with 10% of each sale donated to those in need through our Giving Back initiative. <\/p>","button_text":"Button"}}},"block_order":["8743bf57-6b1a-4f8c-8988-5e42ae277901","a5eb81f9-4c92-4ecc-bf0a-6c9cf53eb6cf","167e640a-03e8-48de-b93f-07bbc26e1244"],"custom_css":["h3 {padding-top: 20px;}"],"settings":{"title":"","center_align":true,"image_height":"fixed","desktop_fixed_height":350,"mobile_fixed_height":250,"section_space":"top_and_bottom"}},"accordion_K3YKGe":{"type":"accordion","blocks":{"accordion_pane_m6HGAA":{"type":"accordion_pane","settings":{"title":"Does the Snow white colour transparent when wet?","content":"<p>We line all our snow white surf suits with a beige econyl sustainable fabric, to prevent them from becoming transparent.<\/p>"}},"accordion_pane_zwBQPA":{"type":"accordion_pane","settings":{"title":"Do your surf suits have built in support?","content":"<p>Our one piece surf suits do not have built in support.  They are double lined and are a firm cut, designed to hold you in.  We have customers from a AA-D that are happy with the support with our surf suits.<\/p>"}},"accordion_pane_cYX4Eg":{"type":"accordion_pane","settings":{"title":"do these surfsuits have adjustable coverage?","content":"<p>You can adjust the fit of each surf suit by hitching the leg high up on your hip, which gives you brief coverage.  Or pull it down on your hip for more coverage.<\/p>"}},"accordion_pane_Py7J3k":{"type":"accordion_pane","settings":{"title":"Which one piece suit provides the most UPF?","content":"<p>If UPF protection is important to you, opt for the darker colours. The Sulawesi in Midnight provides the most UPF block out, due to the dark colour of the fabric and long sleeves.  <\/p>"}},"accordion_pane_ArMU9p":{"type":"accordion_pane","settings":{"title":"What is the fit like on the one piece surf suits?","content":"<p>All our one piece surf suits are designed to be like shape wear and hold you in.  If you prefer a more relaxed feel, size up and if buying the midnight go up two sizes, as the black colour doesn't have as much stretch due to the dying process.<\/p>"}}},"block_order":["accordion_pane_m6HGAA","accordion_pane_zwBQPA","accordion_pane_cYX4Eg","accordion_pane_Py7J3k","accordion_pane_ArMU9p"],"settings":{"title":"FAQS","max_width":100,"allow_multiple":false}},"product-recommendations":{"type":"product-recommendations","custom_css":["div {padding-bottom: 10px;}"],"settings":{"product_recommendations_heading":"You may also like","per_row":4,"limit":8}}},"order":["breadcrumbs","main","210a4ae5-eb6f-4c98-bd15-1c238eaeb22c","1706838275a57a97e2","product-content","ffd7507a-dce2-40e6-af87-0e8a295f7ef6","accordion_K3YKGe","product-recommendations"]}